00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:48.940 align:middle line:84%
I discovered something
really unusual,

00:01:48.940 --> 00:01:51.630 align:middle line:84%
which is that in
quantum physics,

00:01:51.630 --> 00:01:54.940 align:middle line:84%
